Arey LOLU darling, I hope you are a free man. 

Swiggy se daal sabzi aur Mess se roti lekar lunch, тВ╣35 wale pizze se lekar very very fast bowler tak, you exalted to 'Master Lolu'.

Hall 2 ki mitti, OAT ke patthar, Hall 9 ke flowers lekar tune jo gardening therapy krwai, hamesha yaad rhegi. I will miss Moss Rose Purslane. Mauka mila to kabhi dobara krenge.

Apna interaction B-115 se shuru hua, Galaxy ke 2 saal kaafi fun kiye aur last me tu meri ball pe chotil ho gya. Koi nhi, par ball smbhal ke rakhna aur is baar bc trip plan krenge to dhoka mat dena.

Baaki code kro, prof bno, garda uda do bc.

"Varshney, uth jaa. Oye B##%c@@d, daudne chalna hai, uth jaa"

Tera wo hashtag, first year ke end me tere daabe pe inception, Galaxy ke pop-quiz me randomly chale jaana, H4 me saath me stand-up dekhna, sab yaad rhega.

Tab tak Caltech jao, MIT jao aur har baar ki tarah kisi ko btana mat aur apna Defence wala startup kholo, bahut scope hai.

Kaash apan 10 round saath me poore kar paate. I hope there comes a day, when we jog again on the football ground.
